INSERT INTO `residential_buildings_collections` VALUES (1,'of9428bzxvecuy8qm6jqjfav',' Proposed Residential Development at Tuen Mun Town, Lot 520 at Kwun Chui Road, Area 56, Tuen Mun','2025-06-02 10:05:52.021000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.238000',NULL,12,36,'en','Proposed Residential Development at Tuen Mun Town, Lot 520 at Kwun Chui Road, Area 56, Tuen Mun','Shum King Company Limited','06 January 2021 - 31 August 2024','<p>The MORI (凱和山) project in Tuen Mun offers residents the ultimate blend of urban-coastal living, enhanced by the opportunities of the Greater Bay Area.</p><br/><p>The project includes the construction of two 18-storey towers (Towers 1, 2), two 17-storey towers (Towers 3, 5) and sixteen 3-storey houses (Houses 1 to 19) with basements. It has a site area of approximately 12,205 m² , with and maximum gross floor areas of 43,938 m².  </p>'),(3,'hlv4sa6ij76zdsad9r0dpry5','Main Contract Works For the Youth Hostel Project by Po Leung Kuk At Lot No. 4040 in D.D. 120, Ma Tin Pok, Yuen Long (Youth Oasis)','2025-06-02 10:07:05.059000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.056000',NULL,12,36,'en','Main Contract Works For the Youth Hostel Project by Po Leung Kuk At Lot No. 4040 in D.D. 120, Ma Tin Pok, Yuen Long (Youth Oasis)','Po Leung Kuk','08 September 2020 - 06 December 2022','<p>The Hong Kong government launched the &quot;Youth Hostel Scheme&quot; in 2011, which addresses the housing needs of youth in the workforce. It fully funds NGOs to build self-financed hostels on underutilized sites, which includes this Youth Hostel Project by Po Leung Kuk.</p><p>A youth hostel is constructed in Tai Shu Ha Road West, Yuen Long with a 1-storey basement car park, 2 functional storeys, a 1-storey podium, and a 24-storey tower containing 1,248 hostel units, along with a 1-storey M&amp;E floor.</p><p>Scope of work also includes building services installations, sheet piling, excavation, site formation, and foundation work, as well as superstructure elements like planters and retaining walls.</p>'),(5,'pjswrvch5f471czniu363k1c','10-22 Mui Fong Street and 15-19 Kwai Heung Street, Sai Ying Pun for Student Residences for The University of Hong Kong','2025-06-02 10:08:41.061000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.942000',NULL,12,36,'en','10-22 Mui Fong Street and 15-19 Kwai Heung Street, Sai Ying Pun for Student Residences for The University of Hong Kong','The University of Hong Kong','02 April 2019 - 30 June 2022','<p>In July 2018, the Legislative Council (LegCo) Finance Committee (FC) approved a one-off grant for establishing the Higher Education Development Fund (HDF) to expedite the development of student hostels for six University Grants Committee (UGC)-funded universities that were facing shortfalls in hostel places, and The University of Hong Kong (HKU) is one of them.</p><p>On this project for HKU, a multi-storey tower was constructed, providing around 250 student hostel places including 2 storeys of public toilet, 6 nos. of accessible student rooms above podium level. Hostels facilities include common area, management staff accommodation and podium garden and provision of new temporary portable public toilet with related drainage at Mui Fong Street Sitting Out Area.</p>'),(7,'tcu91cf421lzlry5o15y6iio','Main Contract Work for the Proposed Residential Development at Lot No 1066 in D.D. 103, Au Tau, Yuen Long, N.T. (Crescent Green)','2025-06-02 10:10:04.817000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.690000',NULL,12,36,'en','Main Contract Work for the Proposed Residential Development at Lot No 1066 in D.D. 103, Au Tau, Yuen Long, N.T. (Crescent Green)','Power Truth Development Limited','02 July 2018 - 06 November 2020','<p>Crescent Green, located in Kam Tin North, Yuen Long, has a site area of 28,000 sq. m and a floor area of 31,000 sq. m, providing a total of 331 units. The works include superstructure work (9 towers of 13-storey apartments, 29 3-storey houses with basements, as well as a carpark, clubhouse, outdoor pool, and landscaping).</p><p>Crescent Green is strategically located, offering a convenient 4-minute car access to the MTR and connectivity to major bridges and expressways, forming a 30-minute cross-border residential hub between Hong Kong &amp; Shenzhen. The project further benefits from the planned Northern Link rail extension with a new Au Tau Station that will significantly enhance its development potential and connectivity.</p>'),(10,'vcxr4w1z13nsuzg4in5bb8fg','Main Contract of Proposed Composite Development at N.K.I.L. 6534, Junction of Fuk Wing Street, Camp Street & Fuk Wa Street, Sham Shui Po, Kowloon','2025-06-02 10:14:13.370000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.027000',NULL,12,36,'en','Main Contract of Proposed Composite Development at N.K.I.L. 6534, Junction of Fuk Wing Street, Camp Street & Fuk Wa Street, Sham Shui Po, Kowloon','Allied Glory Development Limited','29 January 2018 - 10 February 2021','<p>The scope of work consists of the construction of two 28-storey residential towers with 467 units, 4-level podium, 1-level basement, roof, upper roof, and external works including hard landscape works of the communal garden and play area. Podium includes 1-level clubhouse/ residential lift lobby, 1-level carpark, 1-level government accommodation (Refuse Collection Point)/ loading area, and 1-level plant room. A typical floor includes studio flats, 1-bedroom, 2-bedroom, 3-bedroom, 3-bedroom (with suite/ utility room) with a total 17 flats per floor. The building envelope is cladded with precast façade, stone/glass/ metal cladding, and curtain wall.  </p>'),(12,'eaajrnde7s1kz9nuf31807gu','Proposed Residential Development at No.88 Tuen Mun Heung Sze Wui Road','2025-06-02 10:15:02.830000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.093000',NULL,12,36,'en','Proposed Residential Development at No.88 Tuen Mun Heung Sze Wui Road','Million World Development Limited','15 March 2016 - 31 May 2018','<p>No.88 Tuen Mun Heung Sze Wui Road Project is a Management Contract in which the management services consist of the construction of a 29-storey residential building, offering a total of 100 flats, each with CFA of approximately 99.77sqm.</p><p>The major scope of works comprises of the construction of superstructure works for a single residential tower, including one level of basement (B/F – Sprinkler water and FS water tanks), two podium fl¬oors (G/F &amp; 1/F – Domestic Entrance, Transformer room, Shops), 25 storeys for club house and residential units (2-29/F – club house and 100 nos. residential units) and three roof ¬floors. The scope of works also includes modification and enabling works of the existing R.C. kicker walls and slab. The building envelope is cladded with precast facade and aluminum cladding.</p>'),(14,'mccwoqya6bomaoy7f8i27r83','Management Contract for the Residential Development at No.420-422 Prince Edward Road West','2025-06-02 10:16:00.992000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.604000',NULL,12,36,'en','Management Contract for the Residential Development at No.420-422 Prince Edward Road West','Wise City Investment Limited','29 December 2015 - 14 May 2018','<p>The property is a residential development located at No.420-420 Prince Edward Road West, Kowloon City, Kowloon, Hong Kong. Build King enters into Management Contracts with the client and provides Management Services covering the construction of foundation and ELS works, the subsequent construction of superstructure, MEP, finishing and fitting-out package sub-contract works.</p><p>The major scope of work includes construction of a single 24-storey residential tower, including 4 levels of podium floors, 1 level for pump room and water tank, 17 level of residential floors and 2 levels for recreational facilities and club house. The building envelope of the tower is cladded with wall tiles and aluminum cladding. BIM is adopted in this project for MEP coordination of CSIDs and CBWDs. This project aims to achieve Bronze rating under the BEAM Plus for New Buildings.</p>'),(16,'cu4ohjggaekm8w9q2ep9sifg','Residential development project at 1-17 Sai Yuen Lane, Sai Ying Pun, Hong Kong','2025-06-02 10:17:06.046000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.519000',NULL,12,36,'en','Residential development project at 1-17 Sai Yuen Lane, Sai Ying Pun, Hong Kong','Grace Sky Creation Limited','01 September 2015 - 30 June 2018','<p>The scope of work consists of construction of a single residential tower of 30 storeys high, including 5 levels of podium floor, 25 storeys of residential floors, roof and upper roof. Podium portion includes 2 levels of retail shops and 2 restaurants, 1 level of plant room floor, 1 level of Club House and 1 level of sky garden. A typical floor includes studio flats, 1-bedroom and 2-bedrooms unit at total 10 flats per floor. The building envelope is cladded with pre-cast façade, curtain walling, balcony with glass balustrade, aluminum grille and panel.</p>'),(18,'pw50y7alyezi85pu032wbwvi','Proposed Tseung Kwan O Joint Student Hostel The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology and The Hong Kong Baptist University','2025-06-02 10:20:43.774000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.805000',NULL,12,36,'en','Proposed Tseung Kwan O Joint Student Hostel The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology and The Hong Kong Baptist University','The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology','28 December 2012 - 02 June 2016','<p>To cater for the additional demand for student hostel places arising from the implementation of the four-year undergraduate curriculum and the further development of Hong Kong as a regional education hub, a number of University Grants Committee (UGC)-funded institutions are actively planning student hostel development projects, and the Tseung Kwan O Joint Student Hostel The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology and The Hong Kong Baptist University is one of these developments.</p><p>This 520-place student hostel is a 9 floor building with living accommodation facilities (bedrooms, dining rooms etc) and  common facilities (multi-purpose room &amp; kitchen, study room, gym room, laundry etc.) .  The Sky Garden at the 5th Floor offers a pleasant environment for leisure.</p>'),(20,'mkwupy11z5owfj9n0k5m9bw6','Redevelopment of Disciplined Services Quarters in Fu Tei, Tuen Mun (Contract No. SS A511)','2025-06-02 10:21:45.235000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.167000',NULL,12,36,'en','Redevelopment of Disciplined Services Quarters in Fu Tei, Tuen Mun','Architectural Services Department','18 December 2012 - 14 July 2015','<p>In order to alleviate the shortage of departmental quarters for disciplined services staff, it was proposed to develop the project site in Fu Tei, Tuen Mun into a new departmental quarter.</p><p>Our group was awarded this project and the works include the construction of a 20-storey building block housing 140 quarter unit. The main building contains management office, game centre and other facilities for residents. The main building is connected to the podium floor and garden with a carpark, transformer room, generator room and other facilities. A 11m high noise-barrier was placed at the west of the building to reduce the noise level of the quarters.</p>'),(22,'l04tg4clt7xz5dbjpcbxzre8','Main Contract Works - Proposed Residential Development at T.M.T.L. 334, No. 3 Tsing Yung Street, Tuen Mun, N.T.','2025-06-02 10:23:31.094000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.162000',NULL,12,36,'en','Main Contract Works - Proposed Residential Development at T.M.T.L. 334, No. 3 Tsing Yung Street, Tuen Mun, N.T.','New Accord Ltd.','01 March 2010 - 27 March 2012','<p>This is a residential development project located in Tuen Mun. The project scope includes the construction of a 23-storey high tower block with 21 residential floors and a podium which consists of club house, carparks and entrance lobby. Each floor is 3.5m high for the tower block and the area of the site covered by the tower block on plan is approximately 300m².</p><br/><br/>'),(24,'k5avpcdpz0a18yno45ilrzvm','Carcass Works – Proposed Residential Development at 16-18 Conduit Road, Hong Kong','2025-06-02 10:24:24.827000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.637000',NULL,12,36,'en','Carcass Works – Proposed Residential Development at 16-18 Conduit Road, Hong Kong','Union Art Investment Limited','29 September 2008 - 20 February 2010','<p>The Works consist of the construction of a 17 storeys high tower block on 5 levels of podium</p>'),(26,'fec0dhscg1zagr7lzilvsd89','Carcass Work Contract for Superstructure Works – Phase 7 at Planning Area 19, TCTL 5 MTRC Tung Chung Station Development – Package Three (Contract No. 511/03)','2025-06-02 10:25:52.809000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.400000',NULL,12,36,'en','Carcass Work Contract for Superstructure Works – Phase 7 at Planning Area 19, TCTL 5 MTRC Tung Chung Station Development – Package Three','Claytown Power Enterprises Limited and Cosmos Wide International Limited','13 June 2007 - 14 March 2009','<p>The approximate gross covered floor area is 19,877 m²</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Hoarding and Covered Walkways</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>56 nos. 4 storeys high Town House and 1 Storey Basement (including Pile Caps)</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Clubhouse</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>External Works</li></ul>'),(28,'p2wfv3375appwdbeoi48gyaa','新界屯門第56區管翠路的屯門市地段第520號住宅發展項目','2025-06-03 01:08:57.985000','2025-07-07 07:26:10.914000',NULL,12,36,'zh-Hant-HK','新界屯門第56區管翠路的屯門市地段第520號住宅發展項目','深勁有限公司','2021 年 01 月 06 日 - 2024 年 08 月 31 日','<p>位於屯門的凱和山 (MORI) 發展項目擁有獨特的優勢，能夠為住戶提供都會沿海生活與大灣區發展機遇。</p><p>建築項目包括興建兩幢18層高的大樓(1及2座)、兩幢17層高的大樓(3及5座) 及16座3層高連地庫的獨立屋(1至19座)。總佔地面積約12,205平方米，最大可建總樓面面積為43,938平方米。</p>'),(30,'iwpl2na4n4r4zpx3coznz1m2','保良局元朗馬田壆青年宿舍','2025-06-03 01:10:31.952000','2025-07-07 07:26:12.739000',NULL,12,36,'zh-Hant-HK','保良局元朗馬田壆青年宿舍','保良局','2020 年 09 月 08 日 - 2022 年 12 月 06 日','<p>香港政府於 2011 年推出「青年宿舍計劃」，以解決年輕在職人士的住房需求。該計劃全額資助非政府組織在未盡其用的地點興建自負盈虧的宿舍，保良局元朗馬田壆青年宿舍為其中一項。</p><p>本項目包括於元朗大樹下西路建設一幢青年宿舍，由1層地庫停車場、2層功能樓層、1層平台層、24層大樓組成，大樓內設有1,248個旅舍單元以及1層機電層。</p><p>此項目工程內容包括所有樓宇設備安裝工程、鋼板樁工程、挖掘和側向支撐工程、地盤平整工程、地基以及其他上蓋結構工程，如花槽／擋土牆及沙井等。</p>'),(32,'qpprmx1r0txo23662b5nkk11','西營盤梅芳街10-22號和葵香街15-19號香港大學學生宿舍','2025-06-03 01:11:28.075000','2025-07-07 07:26:14.556000',NULL,12,36,'zh-Hant-HK','西營盤梅芳街10-22號和葵香街15-19號香港大學學生宿舍','香港大學','2019 年 04 月 02 日 - 2022 年 06 月 30 日','<p>2018年7月，立法會財務委員會批准一次性撥款，成立高等教育發展基金，為6所面對宿位短缺的大學教育資助委員會(教資會)資助大學加快興建學生宿舍，香港大學是其中之一。</p><p>此項目為香港大學興建一幢多樓層大樓，提供約250個學生宿舍。宿舍設有2層共用洗手間及6間設在平台樓層以上的無障礙學生房間。宿舍設施包括公共區域、管理人員宿舍及平台花園，並在梅芳街休憩處提供新的臨時流動公共廁所及相關排水設施。</p>'),(34,'opecxitbk4p9qu8ikyps7lah','新界元朗凹頭丈量約份第103約地段第1066號私人住宅發展項目 (山水盈 Crescent Green)','2025-06-03 01:12:08.761000','2025-07-07 07:26:14.154000',NULL,12,36,'zh-Hant-HK','新界元朗凹頭丈量約份第103約地段第1066號私人住宅發展項目 (山水盈 Crescent Green)','威良發展有限公司','2018 年 07 月 02 日 - 2020 年 11 月 06 日','<p>山水盈(Crescent Green)位於元朗錦田北，地盤面積為28,000平方米，樓面面積為31,000平方米，共提供331個單位。項目的工程範圍包括上層結構工程(共9座13層高公寓大樓、29座3層高帶地庫的獨立屋，以及停車場、會所、室外游泳池和景觀綠化)。</p><p>山水盈地理位置優越，約4分鐘車程直達港鐵站，並連接主要橋樑和高速公路，是半小時即可到達的港深跨境生活樞紐。項目更將受惠於正在計劃興建的北環線鐵路延線及新凹頭站，進一步提升其發展潛力和連通性。</p>'),(36,'vi9b2257kozsyux3rlag3hmt','九龍深水埗福榮街、營盤街與福華街交界的新九龍內地段第6534號的綜合發展項目','2025-06-03 01:13:55.236000','2025-07-07 07:26:13.283000',NULL,12,36,'zh-Hant-HK','九龍深水埗福榮街、營盤街與福華街交界的新九龍內地段第6534號的綜合發展項目','滙榮發展有限公司','2018 年 01 月 29 日 - 2021 年 02 月 10 日','<p>工程包括建設兩座28層高住宅大樓，共設有467個單位、4層平台、1層地庫、屋頂、上層屋頂、公用花園及遊樂地方的外圍園景工程。平台包括1層會所/住宅升降機大堂、1 層停車場、1層政府設施（垃圾收集處）/上落貨區、及1 層公共設施房。標準樓層包括開放式住宅單位、一房、兩房、三房單位（連套房/多用途房），每層合共17個單位。建築外層結構使用預製外牆、石板/玻璃/金屬覆蓋層、及幕牆。</p>'),(38,'zvjhxjfmu2lbxoxbx26btwgn','屯門鄉事會路88號住宅發展項目','2025-06-03 01:14:49.709000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.376000',NULL,12,36,'zh-Hant-HK','屯門鄉事會路88號住宅發展項目','民威發展有限公司','2016 年 03 月 15 日 - 2018 年 05 月 31 日','<p>此住宅發展項目位於屯門鄉事會路88號，由利基投得其管理合約，服務内容包括一座29層高的住宅大廈上蓋建造工程。大廈將提供100個建築面積約為99.77平方米的單位。</p><p>工程主要包括建造單幢式住宅大廈，其中包括：1層地下室（地庫 - 灑水器和消防水箱），2層平台（地下及1樓 - 住用入口、變壓器房和商店），25主樓層 （2-29樓 - 會所和100個住宅單位）和3層屋頂。工程同時包括原有的鋼筋混凝土底座牆和板塊等部分的修改和啟用工程。而項目的建築外牆將採用預製外牆和鋁質面板。</p>'),(40,'qxuumnkp67859rjet9fpizxt','太子道西420-422號發展項目工程','2025-06-03 01:18:24.73400