at No.420-422 Prince Edward Road West','Wise City Investment Limited','29 December 2015 - 14 May 2018','<p>The property is a residential development located at No.420-420 Prince Edward Road West, Kowloon City, Kowloon, Hong Kong. Build King enters into Management Contracts with the client and provides Management Services covering the construction of foundation and ELS works, the subsequent construction of superstructure, MEP, finishing and fitting-out package sub-contract works.</p><p>The major scope of work includes construction of a single 24-storey residential tower, including 4 levels of podium floors, 1 level for pump room and water tank, 17 level of residential floors and 2 levels for recreational facilities and club house. The building envelope of the tower is cladded with wall tiles and aluminum cladding. BIM is adopted in this project for MEP coordination of CSIDs and CBWDs. This project aims to achieve Bronze rating under the BEAM Plus for New Buildings.</p>'),(169,'cu4ohjggaekm8w9q2ep9sifg','Residential development project at 1-17 Sai Yuen Lane, Sai Ying Pun, Hong Kong','2025-06-02 10:17:06.046000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.519000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.838000',12,36,'en','Residential development project at 1-17 Sai Yuen Lane, Sai Ying Pun, Hong Kong','Grace Sky Creation Limited','01 September 2015 - 30 June 2018','<p>The scope of work consists of construction of a single residential tower of 30 storeys high, including 5 levels of podium floor, 25 storeys of residential floors, roof and upper roof. Podium portion includes 2 levels of retail shops and 2 restaurants, 1 level of plant room floor, 1 level of Club House and 1 level of sky garden. A typical floor includes studio flats, 1-bedroom and 2-bedrooms unit at total 10 flats per floor. The building envelope is cladded with pre-cast façade, curtain walling, balcony with glass balustrade, aluminum grille and panel.</p>'),(170,'xc14yn4cew2i0ggo0d2la3rg','屯門青榕街3號, 地段 T.M.T.L. 334住宅發展項目工程','2025-06-03 01:26:49.233000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.689000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.976000',12,36,'zh-Hant-HK','屯門青榕街3號, 地段 T.M.T.L. 334住宅發展項目工程','New Accord Ltd.','2010 年 03 月 01 日 - 2012 年 03 月 27 日','<p>位於屯門的住宅發展項目。工程主要包括興建一座23層高大樓，包括21層住宅單位及1 個平臺，設有會所、停車場和入口大廳。樓層高度為3.5米，每層覆蓋的面積約為300平方米。</p>'),(171,'tcu91cf421lzlry5o15y6iio','Main Contract Work for the Proposed Residential Development at Lot No 1066 in D.D. 103, Au Tau, Yuen Long, N.T. (Crescent Green)','2025-06-02 10:10:04.817000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.690000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.040000',12,36,'en','Main Contract Work for the Proposed Residential Development at Lot No 1066 in D.D. 103, Au Tau, Yuen Long, N.T. (Crescent Green)','Power Truth Development Limited','02 July 2018 - 06 November 2020','<p>Crescent Green, located in Kam Tin North, Yuen Long, has a site area of 28,000 sq. m and a floor area of 31,000 sq. m, providing a total of 331 units. The works include superstructure work (9 towers of 13-storey apartments, 29 3-storey houses with basements, as well as a carpark, clubhouse, outdoor pool, and landscaping).</p><p>Crescent Green is strategically located, offering a convenient 4-minute car access to the MTR and connectivity to major bridges and expressways, forming a 30-minute cross-border residential hub between Hong Kong &amp; Shenzhen. The project further benefits from the planned Northern Link rail extension with a new Au Tau Station that will significantly enhance its development potential and connectivity.</p>'),(172,'pw50y7alyezi85pu032wbwvi','Proposed Tseung Kwan O Joint Student Hostel The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology and The Hong Kong Baptist University','2025-06-02 10:20:43.774000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.805000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.136000',12,36,'en','Proposed Tseung Kwan O Joint Student Hostel The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology and The Hong Kong Baptist University','The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology','28 December 2012 - 02 June 2016','<p>To cater for the additional demand for student hostel places arising from the implementation of the four-year undergraduate curriculum and the further development of Hong Kong as a regional education hub, a number of University Grants Committee (UGC)-funded institutions are actively planning student hostel development projects, and the Tseung Kwan O Joint Student Hostel The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology and The Hong Kong Baptist University is one of these developments.</p><p>This 520-place student hostel is a 9 floor building with living accommodation facilities (bedrooms, dining rooms etc) and  common facilities (multi-purpose room &amp; kitchen, study room, gym room, laundry etc.) .  The Sky Garden at the 5th Floor offers a pleasant environment for leisure.</p>'),(173,'vcxr4w1z13nsuzg4in5bb8fg','Main Contract of Proposed Composite Development at N.K.I.L. 6534, Junction of Fuk Wing Street, Camp Street & Fuk Wa Street, Sham Shui Po, Kowloon','2025-06-02 10:14:13.370000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.027000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.224000',12,36,'en','Main Contract of Proposed Composite Development at N.K.I.L. 6534, Junction of Fuk Wing Street, Camp Street & Fuk Wa Street, Sham Shui Po, Kowloon','Allied Glory Development Limited','29 January 2018 - 10 February 2021','<p>The scope of work consists of the construction of two 28-storey residential towers with 467 units, 4-level podium, 1-level basement, roof, upper roof, and external works including hard landscape works of the communal garden and play area. Podium includes 1-level clubhouse/ residential lift lobby, 1-level carpark, 1-level government accommodation (Refuse Collection Point)/ loading area, and 1-level plant room. A typical floor includes studio flats, 1-bedroom, 2-bedroom, 3-bedroom, 3-bedroom (with suite/ utility room) with a total 17 flats per floor. The building envelope is cladded with precast façade, stone/glass/ metal cladding, and curtain wall.  </p>'),(174,'hlv4sa6ij76zdsad9r0dpry5','Main Contract Works For the Youth Hostel Project by Po Leung Kuk At Lot No. 4040 in D.D. 120, Ma Tin Pok, Yuen Long (Youth Oasis)','2025-06-02 10:07:05.059000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.056000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.248000',12,36,'en','Main Contract Works For the Youth Hostel Project by Po Leung Kuk At Lot No. 4040 in D.D. 120, Ma Tin Pok, Yuen Long (Youth Oasis)','Po Leung Kuk','08 September 2020 - 06 December 2022','<p>The Hong Kong government launched the &quot;Youth Hostel Scheme&quot; in 2011, which addresses the housing needs of youth in the workforce. It fully funds NGOs to build self-financed hostels on underutilized sites, which includes this Youth Hostel Project by Po Leung Kuk.</p><p>A youth hostel is constructed in Tai Shu Ha Road West, Yuen Long with a 1-storey basement car park, 2 functional storeys, a 1-storey podium, and a 24-storey tower containing 1,248 hostel units, along with a 1-storey M&amp;E floor.</p><p>Scope of work also includes building services installations, sheet piling, excavation, site formation, and foundation work, as well as superstructure elements like planters and retaining walls.</p>'),(175,'pjswrvch5f471czniu363k1c','10-22 Mui Fong Street and 15-19 Kwai Heung Street, Sai Ying Pun for Student Residences for The University of Hong Kong','2025-06-02 10:08:41.061000','2025-07-07 07:26:15.942000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.323000',12,36,'en','10-22 Mui Fong Street and 15-19 Kwai Heung Street, Sai Ying Pun for Student Residences for The University of Hong Kong','The University of Hong Kong','02 April 2019 - 30 June 2022','<p>In July 2018, the Legislative Council (LegCo) Finance Committee (FC) approved a one-off grant for establishing the Higher Education Development Fund (HDF) to expedite the development of student hostels for six University Grants Committee (UGC)-funded universities that were facing shortfalls in hostel places, and The University of Hong Kong (HKU) is one of them.</p><p>On this project for HKU, a multi-storey tower was constructed, providing around 250 student hostel places including 2 storeys of public toilet, 6 nos. of accessible student rooms above podium level. Hostels facilities include common area, management staff accommodation and podium garden and provision of new temporary portable public toilet with related drainage at Mui Fong Street Sitting Out Area.</p>'),(176,'l04tg4clt7xz5dbjpcbxzre8','Main Contract Works - Proposed Residential Development at T.M.T.L. 334, No. 3 Tsing Yung Street, Tuen Mun, N.T.','2025-06-02 10:23:31.094000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.162000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.338000',12,36,'en','Main Contract Works - Proposed Residential Development at T.M.T.L. 334, No. 3 Tsing Yung Street, Tuen Mun, N.T.','New Accord Ltd.','01 March 2010 - 27 March 2012','<p>This is a residential development project located in Tuen Mun. The project scope includes the construction of a 23-storey high tower block with 21 residential floors and a podium which consists of club house, carparks and entrance lobby. Each floor is 3.5m high for the tower block and the area of the site covered by the tower block on plan is approximately 300m².</p><br/><br/>'),(177,'eaajrnde7s1kz9nuf31807gu','Proposed Residential Development at No.88 Tuen Mun Heung Sze Wui Road','2025-06-02 10:15:02.830000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.093000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.368000',12,36,'en','Proposed Residential Development at No.88 Tuen Mun Heung Sze Wui Road','Million World Development Limited','15 March 2016 - 31 May 2018','<p>No.88 Tuen Mun Heung Sze Wui Road Project is a Management Contract in which the management services consist of the construction of a 29-storey residential building, offering a total of 100 flats, each with CFA of approximately 99.77sqm.</p><p>The major scope of works comprises of the construction of superstructure works for a single residential tower, including one level of basement (B/F – Sprinkler water and FS water tanks), two podium fl¬oors (G/F &amp; 1/F – Domestic Entrance, Transformer room, Shops), 25 storeys for club house and residential units (2-29/F – club house and 100 nos. residential units) and three roof ¬floors. The scope of works also includes modification and enabling works of the existing R.C. kicker walls and slab. The building envelope is cladded with precast facade and aluminum cladding.</p>'),(178,'mkwupy11z5owfj9n0k5m9bw6','Redevelopment of Disciplined Services Quarters in Fu Tei, Tuen Mun (Contract No. SS A511)','2025-06-02 10:21:45.235000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.167000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.422000',12,36,'en','Redevelopment of Disciplined Services Quarters in Fu Tei, Tuen Mun','Architectural Services Department','18 December 2012 - 14 July 2015','<p>In order to alleviate the shortage of departmental quarters for disciplined services staff, it was proposed to develop the project site in Fu Tei, Tuen Mun into a new departmental quarter.</p><p>Our group was awarded this project and the works include the construction of a 20-storey building block housing 140 quarter unit. The main building contains management office, game centre and other facilities for residents. The main building is connected to the podium floor and garden with a carpark, transformer room, generator room and other facilities. A 11m high noise-barrier was placed at the west of the building to reduce the noise level of the quarters.</p>'),(179,'of9428bzxvecuy8qm6jqjfav',' Proposed Residential Development at Tuen Mun Town, Lot 520 at Kwun Chui Road, Area 56, Tuen Mun','2025-06-02 10:05:52.021000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.238000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.441000',12,36,'en','Proposed Residential Development at Tuen Mun Town, Lot 520 at Kwun Chui Road, Area 56, Tuen Mun','Shum King Company Limited','06 January 2021 - 31 August 2024','<p>The MORI (凱和山) project in Tuen Mun offers residents the ultimate blend of urban-coastal living, enhanced by the opportunities of the Greater Bay Area.</p><br/><p>The project includes the construction of two 18-storey towers (Towers 1, 2), two 17-storey towers (Towers 3, 5) and sixteen 3-storey houses (Houses 1 to 19) with basements. It has a site area of approximately 12,205 m² , with and maximum gross floor areas of 43,938 m².  </p>'),(180,'hzsr5vxdjo2r4uo2tl31iscx','東涌地鐵站發展計劃第三期- 上蓋工程裝修合約第七期規劃區編號19 (合約編號 : 511/03)','2025-06-03 01:28:43.702000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.390000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.587000',12,36,'zh-Hant-HK','東涌地鐵站發展計劃第三期- 上蓋工程裝修合約第七期規劃區編號19','Claytown Power Enterprises Limited and Cosmos Wide International Limited','2007 年 06 月 13 日 - 2009 年 03 月 14 日','<p>大約總樓面面積約為 19,877平方米，包括</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>地盤圍板和有蓋行人道</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>樓高4層連地庫的別墅式洋房56個（包括樁帽）</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>會所</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>外部工程</li></ul>'),(181,'dvgjihkcql5txl3096kuhm8i','干德道16-18號建議住宅發展項目的上蓋發展工程','2025-06-03 01:27:37.419000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.478000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.739000',12,36,'zh-Hant-HK','干德道16-18號建議住宅發展項目的上蓋發展工程','Union Art Investment Limited','2008 年 09 月 29 日 - 2010 年 02 月 20 日','<p>該工程包括在5層平台上建造一幢 17層樓高的高層大厦</p>'),(182,'k5avpcdpz0a18yno45ilrzvm','Carcass Works – Proposed Residential Development at 16-18 Conduit Road, Hong Kong','2025-06-02 10:24:24.827000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.637000','2025-07-07 07:26:16.898000',12,36,'en','Carcass Works – Proposed Residential Development at 16-18 Conduit Road, Hong Kong','Union Art Investment Limited','29 September 2008 - 20 February 2010','<p>The Works consist of the construction of a 17 storeys high tower block on 5 levels of podium</p>');
